{
  "stem": "12051.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very prominent man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His-- he used to go to the Yeshiva, to listen to the children, if they learn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was [NON-ENGLISH], you know, the head of the community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anybody that knew him-- he was somebody very special.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think he cannot accept that, that his father, who was somebody so special-- his mother used-- you know, in Czechoslovakia there was a community that there were a lot of poor people, right?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His mother cooked every Thursday for hundred people, specially that they should have a hot meal-- Shabbos?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--before the war-- right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when, God, forbid, she used to mark down how many people came, if there were some missing, she was terribly worried.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened that they didn't come?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he was raised in a very rich home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think it's difficult for him to accept he cannot unite [POINTS] the past with the future.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a certain degree.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it's very difficult that they should understand it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the more they read and the more they hear, the better it is for them to understand it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I tell you honestly, many times, I myself think, is it possible?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did I really go through such hell?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was I really beaten like a dog?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was I really that hungry for three years and cold and-- and destroyed?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the fear, 24 hours of fear-- you cannot-- no picture, no film, no story, no book can portray the actual fear that one lived, that you were sitting all evening long killing lice.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because in your-- you couldn't live like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The clothes-- it was eating you up, and you were just ticking them on your nails.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people were counting, like a joke.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
